        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Meterythrops pictus (Holt and W. Tattersall, 1905). Male (10.5 mm) from western Ireland. (A) Left penis, lateral; (B) left fourth pleopod, posterior; (C) modified seta of fourth pleopod; (D) normal plumose seta of fourth pleopod; (E) left fifth pleopod, posterior. Arrows show the modified seta." ;
